author: Mark Manson
description:
Why do the the liars, the narcissists, and the bullies seem to always win? You see them everywhere: running billion-dollar companies, racking up influence, and walking away with golden parachutes while good people get left behind. In this video, I break down the brutal logic behind why toxic personalities often rise to the top, what history and psychology reveal about their strategies, and how you can succeed without becoming one of them.
